All 23 ready for night watch, sir!

34
00:04:42,181 --> 00:04:43,478
- At ease.
- Yes, sir.

35
00:04:44,717 --> 00:04:46,048
At ease!

36
00:04:49,689 --> 00:04:53,181
Our country faces the sea at three sides,
and all coasts are restricted.

37
00:04:53,826 --> 00:04:57,887
