Something happen with Sun-hwa on break?

249
00:35:32,463 --> 00:35:33,452
Where are you going?

250
00:35:34,465 --> 00:35:37,195
- Seoul.
- What? Hey, Private Kang!

251
00:35:49,046 --> 00:35:52,174
Who is it?

252
00:35:53,951 --> 00:35:56,442
Who is it? You bastard.

253
00:35:57,755 --> 00:36:01,452
Hurry up! Go!

254
00:36:17,975 --> 00:36:22,002
Hey! Private Kang! Pull over!

255
00:36:35,293 --> 00:36:40,959
Are you crazy? Know what you're doing now?
Want to ruin your life?

256
00:36:56,647 --> 00:36:59,878
His mental state is unstable,
so he looks unfit for duty.

257
00:37:01,852 --> 00:37:02,819
- Platoon leader.
- Yes, sir.

258
00:37:03,421 --> 00:37:06,481
- Don't give him a gun.
- I understand, sir.

259
00:37:13,164 --> 00:37:15,724
- Salute.
- Salute.

260
00:37:18,135 --> 00:37:19,033
Reporting, sir.

261
00:37:19,670 --> 00:37:25,609
1st Private Kang Han-chul here to report
that I am unfit for duty,

262
00:37:25,810 --> 00:37:31,407
so on June 15, 2002, I am hereby ordered
to be discharged from my service.

263
00:37:32,083 --> 00:37:33,414
Salute.

264
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:40,350
Take care, Private Kang.

265
00:38:00,311 --> 00:38:01,676
Salute!

266
00:39:53,090 --> 00:39:55,786
- It's so pretty.
- I'm glad we came here.

267
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:57,919
- It's so pretty.
- Let's go in here.

268
00:39:58,496 --> 00:40:02,489
- Hey, we're not supposed to go in there.
- Who cares? Let's just take one picture.

269
00:40:03,134 --> 00:40:05,694
- You're uncontrollable.
- Be careful.

270
00:40:08,239 --> 00:40:10,969
- I told you to wear pants.
- Who cares?

271
00:40:11,108 --> 00:40:14,475
- It's glass.
- What is this?

272
00:40:14,678 --> 00:40:15,474
Be careful.

273
00:40:19,750 --> 00:40:21,547
I'll take it.

274
00:40:22,953 --> 00:40:27,413
I'm taking it.
Smile. One, two, three.

275
00:40:27,725 --> 00:40:30,888
Miss, you can't take pictures here.

276
00:40:31,262 --> 00:40:37,132
- I know, but the scenery is so pretty.
- And we came all the way from Seoul.

277
00:40:38,903 --> 00:40:42,395
- Then take just one picture.
- Take it with both of us.

278
00:40:43,974 --> 00:40:45,100
Here I go.

279
00:40:45,443 --> 00:40:49,436
- Smile. One, two...
- Wait.

280
00:40:51,015 --> 00:40:53,415
I'm taking it. One, Two...

281
00:40:54,919 --> 00:40:58,855
- Anyway, who put that glass there?
- It's for the spies.

282
00:40:59,089 --> 00:41:02,581
- But I got cut.
- Glass shouldn't be there.

283
00:41:02,660 --> 00:41:05,128
- Private Kim!
- Sir, everything is clear!

284
00:41:05,229 --> 00:41:08,460
Clear? Who told these girls to come
in here and take pictures?

285
00:41:09,133 --> 00:41:12,534
Ladies, this is a restricted zone.
No pictures here.

286
00:41:12,670 --> 00:41:15,901
We're not spies.
What are you doing?

287
00:41:16,507 --> 00:41:20,603
- We have other pictures, you know.
- Be grateful we're not arresting you.

288
00:41:24,014 --> 00:41:28,542
You careless bastard. Wanna go to detention?
Do your duty right!

289
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:39,755
Stop coming back here.
Get out of there.

290
00:41:43,367 --> 00:41:44,356
Give me the gun!

291
00:41:47,705 --> 00:41:48,694
Young-gil.

292
00:41:50,875 --> 00:41:52,103
Young-gil.

293
00:42:12,830 --> 00:42:14,058
Young-gil.

294
00:42:24,675 --> 00:42:25,835
What the hell?

295
00:42:31,682 --> 00:42:35,252
You go back in first.
I'll go take her home.

296
00:42:35,252 --> 00:42:38,619
She's that crazy fish vendor's sister.
He'll kill you.

297
00:42:38,689 --> 00:42:41,522
Don't worry, idiot.
Just give me the ball.

298
00:42:44,562 --> 00:42:45,256
Hurry and go.
Here.

299
00:43:14,558 --> 00:43:15,684
Where'd you get that?

300
00:43:58,202 --> 00:43:58,998
Who's there?

301
00:44:01,038 --> 00:44:05,031
Miss. What are you doing here?
It's dangerous, so go.

302
00:44:07,778 --> 00:44:10,645
Give it back.
Hey! Hey!

303
00:44:41,478 --> 00:44:42,240
What?

304
00:44:45,115 --> 00:44:45,911
What is that?

305
00:44:46,950 --> 00:44:50,681
Hey. Why do you have this?

306
00:45:16,380 --> 00:45:19,611
Private Kim. Want to hear a fun story?

307
00:45:22,486 --> 00:45:24,784
While carrying
the infantry's password back,

308
00:45:25,489 --> 00:45:29,789
- that fish vendor's crazy sister kept smiling at me.
- So what?

309
00:45:32,329 --> 00:45:34,092
No, just that she smiled.

310
00:45:35,532 --> 00:45:39,992
- Is that all she did?
- Stop asking, it's embarrassing.

311
00:45:41,772 --> 00:45:45,037
- Rainbow!
- It's me.

312
00:45:47,111 --> 00:45:48,009
Hey, Private Kim.

313
00:45:49,012 --> 00:45:54,712
Private Kang. What are you doing here
in your uniform? You scared me.

314
00:45:58,055 --> 00:46:01,252
- I came here on a weird intuition.
- What intuition?

315
00:46:03,193 --> 00:46:05,058
- Give me your gun.
- Don't give it to him.

316
00:46:06,964 --> 00:46:09,330
Give it back,
or else we go to detention.

317
00:46:16,840 --> 00:46:21,140
If Platoon Leader finds out, we're dead.
Hurry and go back.

318
00:46:23,914 --> 00:46:24,710
To where?

319
00:46:26,717 --> 00:46:27,274
What?

320
00:46:32,623 --> 00:46:37,151
- You can't enter.
- It's me, Private Kang. Remember?

321
00:46:37,261 --> 00:46:40,492
Please stop doing this.
You were discharged a while ago.

322
00:46:40,864 --> 00:46:43,765
- Who was discharged?
- Don't do this, and go back home.

323
00:46:43,834 --> 00:46:47,270
I haven't finished my service yet.
I have a year left.

324
00:46:47,504 --> 00:46:48,198
What's going on?

325
00:46:48,405 --> 00:46:52,671
Sir, he keeps saying he's here for duty.

326
00:46:53,010 --> 00:46:53,704
Salute.

327
00:46:54,244 --> 00:46:58,078
- 1st Private Kang Han-chul here for duty.
- Kang Han-chul, wake up!

328
00:46:58,315 --> 00:47:00,283
Platoon Leader, I'm fine.

329
00:47:01,652 --> 00:47:04,280
- We'll get into trouble, so never let him in.
- I understand, sir.

330
00:47:07,624 --> 00:47:12,687
Open it. Open it, Private Kim!
Open it!

331
00:47:21,271 --> 00:47:23,239
- Salute.
- Salute.

332
00:47:24,341 --> 00:47:27,071
Coast Guard Platoon.
22 soldiers reporting and one on duty.

333
00:47:27,311 --> 00:47:29,108
All 22 prepared for night watch, sir!

334
00:47:30,581 --> 00:47:31,206
Dispatch to duties.

335
00:47:33,116 --> 00:47:34,140
About-face.

336
00:47:36,086 --> 00:47:37,519
Raise your arms.

